This amendment to IEEE Std 802.1D, 1998 edition is intended to document maintenance items identified in the text of IEEE Std 802.1D, 1998 edition (ISO/IEC 15802-3:1998). The document identifies any proposed changes to the text that have arisen as a consequence of maintenance activity. These are documented in the usual form for amendments to IEEE 802(R) standards; i.e., as an explicit set of editing instructions that, if correctly applied to the text of ISO/IEC 15802-3:1998, will create a corrected document.